ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this course - provided the student is interested in game theory, formal modeling, and is enthusiastic about spending about 10 hours per week trying to solve problem sets...
See my answer to the first question.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: After one semester of game theory, I have figured out that I have started to think in terms of best responses, payoffs, profitable deviations etc. - which definitely helped me clarify my thinking!
